{"tid":1340593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家可以冷靜啲分析現況，有巴打話聽日就臨政","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:15:40.000Z","uid":272454,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e9992388b28f8ef9492a791b2f9e085a5ba5fbc","tid":1340593,"uid":272454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"p牌講野，自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n土共手段一向就是民眾鬥民眾<br />\n<br />\n見到元朗我地個個都好嬲<br />\n但係依家呢個時候是否真的適合成立臨政？<br />\n<br />\n1.我地有幾多物資？可以頂到幾耐？<br />\n對方有真槍實彈，對方有大範圍網絡監控<br />\n老解可以攞黎，可以坦克車。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地冇外國軍支援既情況下可以頂幾耐？<br />\n我地點樣比外國軍插手機會？<br />\n文宣左先定係臨政左先好？<br />\n如果要外國插手，咩情況下最快最有效？<br />\n<br />\n明天是否適合打入元朗？<br />\n黑黑相照，黑社會散場黑警就會拉我地人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係反對，我係想確認大家有冇失去理智，而心急左<br />\n<br />\n請理性巴絲幫手冷靜分析現在情況，看清大局何在。<br />\n<br />\n只要可以令香港贏我就一定支持。"},{"pid":"974b87b92f1567638304e0685d8ca899bc7fa362","tid":1340593,"uid":272454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d28c3d66d905afd6ca0976a6d9bf3a4ecd5dc3","tid":1340593,"uid":272454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea4b590cb8b2c21cf0c114e81998f8d306889d5","tid":1340593,"uid":272454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ba8632f2cae6232b8f050260c4a577b200d2e6","tid":1340593,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"黑社會黎，打<br />\n黑警黎，照打<br />\n<br />\n打輸，你做乜都冇用，因為人地總可以發爛，打到你卜街就贏。"},{"pid":"aa298224f1bed39e7a59647f07a8ef0f6980fa20"